---
import Layout from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Layout title="Vault — System Assets | Thee Rainers">
  <Fragment slot="head">
    <meta name="description" content="Systemic performance blueprints. Footwork, shadowboxing, and the complete operating system for fighters who think in structures — not reps." />
  </Fragment>

  <section class="min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-32 md:py-40">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">

      <div class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The System</p>
        <h1 class="font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter text-5xl md:text-7xl leading-[0.8] mb-8">Greatness<br/>is engineered.</h1>
        <p class="text-white/40 text-base max-w-[480px] leading-relaxed">Three entry points into the methodology. Each a component. All built for fighters who think in structures, not sessions.</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 60/40 Product Grid -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-[3fr_2fr] gap-[2px]">

        <!-- Left 60%: Bundle — Flagship -->
        <div class="bg-[#0D1F1F] border border-[#D4A373]/20 hover:border-[#D4A373]/55 transition-colors duration-300 p-12 md:p-16 flex flex-col justify-between min-h-[540px] group">
          <div>
            <span class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase">Complete System · Best Value</span>
            <h2 class="font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter mt-4 mb-6 text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-[0.85]">The Rainers<br/>Bundle</h2>
            <p class="text-white/50 text-sm leading-relaxed max-w-[380px] mb-10">Footwork + Shadowboxing. 106 drill rounds. The complete operating system — spatial geometry and kinetic chain trained in sequence. Not sold separately at this price.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-col gap-3">
              <p class="text-white/25 text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-2">Includes</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">— Everything in the Footwork Blueprint</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">— Everything in the Shadowboxing Blueprint</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">— Spatial geometry and kinetic chain trained in sequence</p>
              <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">— A self-sufficient system operable without a coach present</p>
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-sm">— Monthly Live Q&A access</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="mt-12 flex items-center justify-between">
            <span class="text-white font-black text-4xl">$87</span>
            <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/14A4gz59hgxUaa65006J20m" target="_blank"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center font-bold border-2 border-[#D4A373] text-[#D4A373] bg-transparent px-10 py-4 text-sm tracking-widest uppercase transition-all duration-200 hover:bg-[#D4A373] hover:text-black">
              Get the System →
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Right 40%: Individual Blueprints stacked -->
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-[2px]">

          <!-- Footwork Blueprint -->
          <div class="bg-[#111111] border border-white/5 hover:border-[#D4A373]/20 transition-colors duration-300 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between flex-1 group">
            <div>
              <span class="text-white/30 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase">Blueprint · Module 01</span>
              <h3 class="font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tight mt-3 mb-3 text-xl leading-tight">Footwork<br/>Blueprint</h3>
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">56 rounds. The four bases. Distance, angles, exits. The platform that everything else runs on.</p>
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">+ Monthly Q&A</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-8">
              <span class="text-white/60 font-bold text-lg">$47</span>
              <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/bJe14n8lt81ogyu3VW6J20k" target="_blank"
                class="text-[#D4A373] text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
                Buy →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Shadowboxing Blueprint -->
          <div class="bg-[#111111] border border-white/5 hover:border-[#D4A373]/20 transition-colors duration-300 p-10 flex flex-col justify-between flex-1 group">
            <div>
              <span class="text-white/30 text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase">Blueprint · Module 02</span>
              <h3 class="font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tight mt-3 mb-3 text-xl leading-tight">Shadowboxing<br/>Blueprint</h3>
              <p class="text-white/40 text-xs leading-relaxed mb-3">Skill tests, rhythm, range control. The kinetic chain applied in motion without external pressure.</p>
              <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">+ Monthly Q&A</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center justify-between mt-8">
              <span class="text-white/60 font-bold text-lg">$47</span>
              <a href="https://buy.stripe.com/5kQdR91X5dlIeqm8cc6J20l" target="_blank"
                class="text-[#D4A373] text-xs font-bold tracking-widest uppercase hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">
                Buy →
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- SEO anchor: Systemic Performance -->
      <div class="mt-28 border-t border-white/5 pt-16 grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-12">
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Systemic Performance</p>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every blueprint is a component of a larger system. The goal is not to complete the drill. The goal is to automate the pattern under pressure.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">Autonomic Regulation</p>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">When the nervous system is trained correctly, execution becomes autonomous. That is the difference between a fighter who performs and one who survives.</p>
        </div>
        <div>
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-4">1 of 1 Output</p>
          <p class="text-white/40 text-sm leading-relaxed">These blueprints are the entry point. The ceiling is Private Architecture — a system built entirely around your mechanics. <a href="/command" class="text-[#D4A373] hover:opacity-60 transition-opacity duration-200">Apply here.</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Backbone -->
  <section class="bg-[#0A0A0A] px-8 md:px-16 lg:px-24 py-24 border-t border-white/5">
    <div class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto w-full">

      <div class="mb-16">
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[11px] tracking-widest uppercase mb-6">The Foundation</p>
        <h2 class="font-black text-white uppercase tracking-tighter text-4xl md:text-5xl leading-[0.85] max-w-[480px]">Seven virtues.<br/>Seven levers.<br/>One system.</h2>
      </div>

      <div class="flex flex-col divide-y divide-white/5">

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Diligence</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Cue Reading</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"Watch and pray" — Mt 26:41</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Chastity</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Kinetic Chain</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"Whatever you do, work at it with all your heart" — Col 3:23</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Fortitude</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Reactive Stiffness</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"They will run and not grow weary" — Is 40:31</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Temperance</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Range Fluency</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"I have become all things to all people" — 1 Cor 9:22</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Justice</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Defensive Responsibility</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"Put on the full armor of God" — Eph 6:11–13</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Faith</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Transfer to Live</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"Be doers of the word, not hearers only" — Jas 1:22</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-[1fr_1fr_1fr] py-8 items-start gap-6 tr-card">
          <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">Humility</p>
          <p class="text-white/50 text-sm">Identity & Presence</p>
          <p class="text-white/25 text-xs leading-relaxed italic">"I have fought the good fight, I have finished the race" — 2 Tim 4:7</p>
        </div>

      </div>

      <div class="mt-20 border-t border-white/5 pt-16">
        <p class="font-black text-white/10 uppercase tracking-tighter text-3xl md:text-4xl leading-[0.9] max-w-[640px]">"I do not run aimlessly. I do not box as one beating the air. I discipline my body and keep it under control."</p>
        <p class="text-[#D4A373] text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase mt-6">1 Corinthians 9:26–27</p>
      </div>

    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
